1
00:00:07,400 --> 00:00:11,460
♪Just To Meet You, you fell for me♪

2
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:15,460
♪Just to meet me, into my trap you fell♪

3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:19,240
♪Wanna try a breathless love?♪

4
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:23,490
♪Every move hits the heart, close and sure♪

5
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:27,460
♪Just To Meet You, you love my playful charm♪

6
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:31,480
♪Just to meet me,
my romantic little schemes for you♪

7
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:35,170
♪Wanna play another brand-new game?♪

8
00:00:35,170 --> 00:00:40,360
♪Layer by layer, we close the gap♪

9
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:47,060
=Just To Meet You=

10
00:00:47,100 --> 00:00:48,140
=Episode 10=
=Love Elope=

11
00:00:48,140 --> 00:00:48,700
=Save the Lis=

12
00:00:50,920 --> 00:00:52,560
(That person sent over Xiaodi's photo,)

13
00:00:52,790 --> 00:00:54,240
(saying Xiaodi is safe.)

14
00:00:54,710 --> 00:00:57,000
(Are they waiting for me to hurt Ye Lang?)

15
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:59,350
(If I still can't find any clues,)

16
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:00,480
(could it be...)

17
00:01:04,950 --> 00:01:05,870
We're here.

18
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:27,120
Where are we?

19
00:01:29,070 --> 00:01:30,120
(This was our home)

20
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:31,070
(in the previous life.)

21
00:01:32,310 --> 00:01:33,150
What do you think?

22
00:01:33,510 --> 00:01:34,350
Do you like it?

23
00:01:34,430 --> 00:01:35,270
Mm.

24
00:02:03,590 --> 00:02:04,560
This place

25
00:02:05,430 --> 00:02:06,760
has everything I love.

26
00:02:12,030 --> 00:02:13,870
(Because every single thing here)

27
00:02:13,870 --> 00:02:16,030
(was picked by us in our previous life.)

28
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,520
Thank you

29
00:02:19,430 --> 00:02:20,430
for making a home for me,

30
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:23,190
a home I truly love.

31
00:02:24,430 --> 00:02:25,270
Don't worry.

32
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:28,630
This is a home just for us.

33
00:02:34,190 --> 00:02:35,560
(Xiaodi.)

34
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:36,710
(Forgive my selfishness.)

35
00:02:37,150 --> 00:02:37,990
(Wait a bit longer.)

36
00:02:38,430 --> 00:02:39,270
(I promise.)

37
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:54,840
Ye Lang,

38
00:02:55,310 --> 00:02:56,470
come down for breakfast.

39
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:15,920
Niannian.

40
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:17,520
I...

41
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,720
I need a morning kiss.

42
00:03:19,910 --> 00:03:20,750
Otherwise,

43
00:03:21,430 --> 00:03:22,790
I won't have any appetite all day.

44
00:03:32,870 --> 00:03:33,710
Niannian.

45
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,520
Being with you

46
00:03:37,030 --> 00:03:38,190
really makes me happy.

47
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:42,310
If you want to stay with me forever,

48
00:03:43,310 --> 00:03:44,800
then win over my stomach.

49
00:04:08,310 --> 00:04:09,240
That's perfect.

50
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,280
Then your personal chef

51
00:04:14,870 --> 00:04:16,480
will make my best dish for you.

52
00:04:18,230 --> 00:04:19,100
Give me a hand.

53
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:19,960
Okay.

54
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:22,760
Pass me an onion.

55
00:04:25,950 --> 00:04:27,800
Do you want a red onion,

56
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,000
or

57
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,070
a white one?

58
00:04:30,070 --> 00:04:31,940
(1 Notification)

59
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:40,240
(Li Group's stock
has been falling for three days.)

60
00:04:40,510 --> 00:04:42,160
(It hit the down limit at open.)

61
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:44,430
(No way out for retail investors.)

62
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,520
Ye Lang.

63
00:04:48,390 --> 00:04:49,230
Ye Lang.

64
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:54,680
What was I about to say?

65
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:57,950
Do you want to go back?

66
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,440
No need.

67
00:05:05,510 --> 00:05:06,350
Nothing matters

68
00:05:07,750 --> 00:05:09,070
more than cooking for you.

69
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,800
(Stay close to Ye Lang.)

70
00:05:20,270 --> 00:05:21,630
(Don't do anything rash.)

71
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,870
(What is he really after?)

72
00:05:24,750 --> 00:05:25,720
(Ye Lang.)

73
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:26,630
(What should I do?)

74
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:33,790
Brother.

75
00:05:37,310 --> 00:05:38,150
Come home with me.

76
00:05:39,070 --> 00:05:39,910
Which home?

77
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:44,190
I know you're still at odds with Father
because of Ms. Jiang.

78
00:05:45,190 --> 00:05:46,560
You've seen the news.

79
00:05:47,510 --> 00:05:48,800
Father was even hospitalized.

80
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:52,600
Only you can save tomorrow's
shareholders' meeting.

81
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:55,590
Finished?

82
00:05:59,430 --> 00:06:01,480
Brother. I'll be waiting for you tomorrow.

83
00:06:05,190 --> 00:06:06,030
Ye Lang.

84
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,120
Tomorrow's big show

85
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,920
won't start without you.

86
00:06:40,070 --> 00:06:41,070
Wait here for me.

87
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:50,510
Mr. Li, let me be blunt.

88
00:06:50,830 --> 00:06:52,270
The stock hit limit-down at open.

89
00:06:52,630 --> 00:06:53,720
Who's going to

90
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,640
cover our losses?

91
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:56,790
Yeah. Last week, you said

92
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:59,000
the new smart prosthetics tech was your ace.

93
00:06:59,000 --> 00:06:59,860
So how did it end up

94
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:01,240
a material at a rival's launch?

95
00:07:01,270 --> 00:07:03,830
Mr. Li always prized the study.

96
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:06,310
All confidential files
kept in the main residence.

97
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,200
Turns out

98
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,430
you got hit

99
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:09,630
by our own people.

100
00:07:10,070 --> 00:07:10,910
Everyone,

101
00:07:11,510 --> 00:07:12,390
please stay calm.

102
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:13,590
The board

103
00:07:13,950 --> 00:07:15,360
will fully investigate

104
00:07:15,750 --> 00:07:17,000
the tech leak.

105
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:18,800
Give me another three days.

106
00:07:20,070 --> 00:07:20,910
Three days?

107
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:22,720
Till the stock becomes worthless?

108
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,640
Young Master

109
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:26,000
was all glory at the engagement party.

110
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:28,480
What, did love cloud your judgment?

111
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:30,440
Calm down please.

112
00:07:30,950 --> 00:07:33,240
This has nothing to do with my brother.

113
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:34,560
There must be a mole.

114
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:37,320
Nonsense.

115
00:07:40,870 --> 00:07:41,710
Brother,

116
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:42,800
just tell the truth.

117
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:46,160
The fingerprint access log only shows you.

118
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,830
Don't forsake family business for that woman.

119
00:07:50,270 --> 00:07:51,720
Our family can't be ruined by you.

120
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,470
Master, please stop.

121
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,680
Young Master was fooled by that woman.

122
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,190
I saw it clearly

123
00:07:58,510 --> 00:08:00,360
Jiang Niannian was sneaking by the study.

124
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,680
Master, please see the truth.

125
00:08:01,750 --> 00:08:02,590
Ye Lang.

126
00:08:03,190 --> 00:08:04,040
How could you

127
00:08:04,390 --> 00:08:05,680
let the wolf into the house!

128
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,000
Father.

129
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,310
Don't get so worked up.

130
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,200
Brother,

131
00:08:10,430 --> 00:08:11,750
I know you're protecting her.

132
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:13,830
What if she really did that?

133
00:08:14,430 --> 00:08:15,750
I know you clearly draw the line.

134
00:08:16,270 --> 00:08:17,510
You won't cover for her.

135
00:08:18,270 --> 00:08:19,110
Right?

136
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,720
You unfilial son!

137
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,080
Stop!

138
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:27,760
Why are you here?

139
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:38,350
Master Li.

140
00:08:39,150 --> 00:08:40,320
It was me who entered

141
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:41,840
the study.

142
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,080
Ye Lang.

143
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,750
You heard her?

144
00:08:46,390 --> 00:08:47,240
She's a spy

145
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:49,120
sent by the Ming family!

146
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,160
Dad.

147
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,480
She's not a spy.

148
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,750
I told her to go to the study.

149
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,680
What?

150
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,030
Brother, you're saying

151
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,440
she's not a spy,

152
00:08:59,460 --> 00:09:00,440
then she is the insider?

153
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,560
Ye Lang.

154
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:07,320
Even if you're my own son,

155
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,750
if you ruin the Li family,

156
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:12,080
I won't go easy on you.

157
00:09:13,790 --> 00:09:14,630
Mr. Li.

158
00:09:15,790 --> 00:09:17,150
I know what I should do

159
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:18,240
and what I shouldn't.

160
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:43,990
♪Stitched-up lips
tear open a blood-red dusk♪

161
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:52,010
♪You return reborn,
seeing through all my cracks♪

162
00:09:52,560 --> 00:09:59,560
♪This tenderness, a trap or a gift?♪

163
00:10:00,310 --> 00:10:02,780
♪Still, I'd wager my next life on it♪

164
00:10:02,780 --> 00:10:07,780
♪Just for a moment to recognize you again♪

165
00:10:07,780 --> 00:10:12,010
♪You are the blazing light in my despair♪

166
00:10:12,520 --> 00:10:16,450
♪Lighting the edges of my frozen wings♪

167
00:10:16,500 --> 00:10:20,290
♪I burn myself,
leaping into an illusion of fire♪

168
00:10:20,290 --> 00:10:26,040
♪Breaking free
from dead vines in the ashes♪

169
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:30,360
♪You are the brightest star in the night♪

170
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:34,220
♪Awakening my dormant fate♪

171
00:10:34,230 --> 00:10:38,720
♪Freeing me from this half-life prison♪

172
00:10:38,750 --> 00:10:43,580
♪As the bells shatter the past♪

173
00:10:43,980 --> 00:10:50,520
♪Life finds its way again♪
